message: 對 OpenBudget or OpenSpending 議題有興趣的，不妨參加 7/30 由 Open Government Partnership 舉辦的 webminar，將會介紹 Global Initiative for Fiscal Transparency (GIFT)
story: Chia-Kai Liu shared a link to the group: g0v.tw 後勤中心.
description: The Open Government Partnership and the Global Initiative for Fiscal Transparency is pleased to announce a webinar to introduce the OGP Fiscal Openness Working Group on Tuesday, July 30, 2013 at 8:00 am EST. We hope you can join us. Please
name: Webinar to introduce the OGP Fiscal Openness Working Group
